---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="About | Financial Tools by Jeremie Joseph Bornais"
	description="Financial Tools is created by Jeremie Joseph Bornais, a software developer and licensed life insurance agent in Ontario, Canada."
>
	<div>
		<div class="mb-8">
			<a
				href={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}`}
				class="inline-flex items-center text-sm font-medium text-slate-500 transition-colors hover:text-amber-600"
			>
				<svg class="mr-1 h-4 w-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7" /></svg>
				Back to all tools
			</a>
		</div>

		<h1 class="font-display text-3xl leading-tight text-slate-900 sm:text-4xl">About</h1>

		<!-- Creator -->
		<section class="mt-8 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 sm:p-8">
			<div class="flex flex-col gap-5 sm:flex-row sm:items-start">
				<img
					src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}headshot.webp`}
					alt="Jeremie Joseph Bornais"
					class="h-24 w-24 shrink-0 rounded-full object-cover shadow-sm"
				/>
				<div>
					<h2 class="font-display text-xl text-slate-900">Jeremie Joseph Bornais</h2>
					<p class="mt-0.5 text-sm text-amber-700 font-medium">Software Developer &amp; Licensed Life Insurance Agent, Ontario</p>
					<p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-600">
						I built this site to give Ontario residents a simple, private way to get a ballpark sense of their financial needs without having to share their data with anyone or sit through a sales call. More tools will be added over time.
					</p>
					<p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-600">
						As a licensed life insurance agent in Ontario, I understand these calculations firsthand. That said, every person's situation is different. These tools are meant to be a starting point, not a substitute for personalized service. If you want to talk through your specific circumstances, I'm happy to help.
					</p>

					<div class="mt-5 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
						<a
							href="https://jeremie.bornais.ca"
							target="_blank"
							rel="noopener noreferrer"
							class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 px-3 py-2 text-sm text-slate-700 transition-colors hover:border-amber-300 hover:text-amber-700"
						>
							<svg class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6m0 0v6m0-6L10 14" /></svg>
							jeremie.bornais.ca
						</a>
						<a
							href="mailto:jeremie@bornais.ca"
							class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 px-3 py-2 text-sm text-slate-700 transition-colors hover:border-amber-300 hover:text-amber-700"
						>
							<svg class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3 8l7.89 5.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z" /></svg>
							jeremie@bornais.ca
						</a>
						<a
							href="https://github.com/jere-mie"
							target="_blank"
							rel="noopener noreferrer"
							class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 px-3 py-2 text-sm text-slate-700 transition-colors hover:border-amber-300 hover:text-amber-700"
						>
							<svg class="h-4 w-4" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 2C6.477 2 2 6.484 2 12.017c0 4.425 2.865 8.18 6.839 9.504.5.092.682-.217.682-.483 0-.237-.008-.868-.013-1.703-2.782.605-3.369-1.343-3.369-1.343-.454-1.158-1.11-1.466-1.11-1.466-.908-.62.069-.608.069-.608 1.003.07 1.531 1.032 1.531 1.032.892 1.53 2.341 1.088 2.91.832.092-.647.35-1.088.636-1.338-2.22-.253-4.555-1.113-4.555-4.951 0-1.093.39-1.988 1.029-2.688-.103-.253-.446-1.272.098-2.65 0 0 .84-.27 2.75 1.026A9.564 9.564 0 0112 6.844c.85.004 1.705.115 2.504.337 1.909-1.296 2.747-1.027 2.747-1.027.546 1.379.202 2.398.1 2.651.64.7 1.028 1.595 1.028 2.688 0 3.848-2.339 4.695-4.566 4.943.359.309.678.92.678 1.855 0 1.338-.012 2.419-.012 2.747 0 .268.18.58.688.482A10.019 10.019 0 0022 12.017C22 6.484 17.522 2 12 2z" /></svg>
							github.com/jere-mie
						</a>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- About this project -->
		<section class="mt-6 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 sm:p-8">
			<h2 class="font-display text-xl text-slate-900">About this project</h2>
			<p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-600">
				This site is an open-source collection of free, browser-based calculators for personal finance. All tools run entirely in your browser. Nothing you enter is ever sent to a server or stored anywhere.
			</p>
			<p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-600">
				More tools are planned. If you have a suggestion or want to contribute, the source code is available on GitHub.
			</p>
			<div class="mt-5">
				<a
					href="https://github.com/jere-mie/financial-tools"
					target="_blank"
					rel="noopener noreferrer"
					class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 px-3 py-2 text-sm text-slate-700 transition-colors hover:border-amber-300 hover:text-amber-700"
				>
					<svg class="h-4 w-4" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 2C6.477 2 2 6.484 2 12.017c0 4.425 2.865 8.18 6.839 9.504.5.092.682-.217.682-.483 0-.237-.008-.868-.013-1.703-2.782.605-3.369-1.343-3.369-1.343-.454-1.158-1.11-1.466-1.11-1.466-.908-.62.069-.608.069-.608 1.003.07 1.531 1.032 1.531 1.032.892 1.53 2.341 1.088 2.91.832.092-.647.35-1.088.636-1.338-2.22-.253-4.555-1.113-4.555-4.951 0-1.093.39-1.988 1.029-2.688-.103-.253-.446-1.272.098-2.65 0 0 .84-.27 2.75 1.026A9.564 9.564 0 0112 6.844c.85.004 1.705.115 2.504.337 1.909-1.296 2.747-1.027 2.747-1.027.546 1.379.202 2.398.1 2.651.64.7 1.028 1.595 1.028 2.688 0 3.848-2.339 4.695-4.566 4.943.359.309.678.92.678 1.855 0 1.338-.012 2.419-.012 2.747 0 .268.18.58.688.482A10.019 10.019 0 0022 12.017C22 6.484 17.522 2 12 2z" /></svg>
					View source on GitHub
				</a>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- Disclaimer -->
		<section class="mt-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 p-5 sm:p-6">
			<div class="flex items-start gap-3">
				<svg class="mt-0.5 h-5 w-5 shrink-0 text-slate-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13 16h-1v-4h-1m1-4h.01M12 2a10 10 0 100 20 10 10 0 000-20z" /></svg>
				<div class="text-xs leading-relaxed text-slate-500 sm:text-sm">
					<p class="font-semibold text-slate-600">Disclaimer</p>
					<p class="mt-1">
						The tools on this site are provided for <strong>educational and informational purposes only</strong> and do not constitute personalized financial, insurance, or professional advice. While Jeremie Joseph Bornais is a licensed life insurance agent in Ontario, Canada, nothing on this site constitutes a recommendation or solicitation specific to your situation. Results are estimates based on general assumptions. Please consult a qualified professional before making any financial or insurance decisions.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>
	</div>
</Layout>
